Sequence Information.Family: Belongs to the frog skin active peptide family (Brevinin subfamily)
Sequence Information.Hemolytic Activity: [Ref.9784389] Have no detectable hemolytic activity at aconcentration of 20µg/ml against human red blood cell.
Sequence Information.Cytotoxicity: No cytotoxicity information found in the reference(s) presented
Sequence Information.Function: Antibacterial activity against Gram-positive bacterium S.aureus. Has no detectable hemolytic activity.
